Of course, in the medical&nbsp;
science, it is not mentioned.

00:27:04.320 --> 00:27:06.960
But we have plexuses,

00:27:06.960 --> 00:27:13.200
and all these plexuses that we&nbsp;
know of, on a physical level,

00:27:13.200 --> 00:27:17.640
are acted upon by these centres.

