00:27:34.360 --> 00:27:40.840
But this is the science of totality, of the whole,

00:27:40.840 --> 00:27:52.680
where you have to trigger an energy&nbsp;
which is lying in the sacrum bone.

00:27:52.680 --> 00:27:53.320
Just imagine!

00:27:53.320 --> 00:27:56.720
It was called sacrum by the Greeks,

00:27:56.720 --> 00:27:58.820
meaning they knew it’s a sacred bone.

00:27:58.820 --> 00:28:03.000
Or why did they call it a sacred bone?

00:28:03.000 --> 00:28:10.040
This energy to pass through all these centres

00:28:10.040 --> 00:28:19.600
to integrate them, to nourish&nbsp;
them, and to enlighten them,

00:28:19.600 --> 00:28:23.240
and ultimately to break&nbsp;
through your fontanel bone area

00:28:23.240 --> 00:28:26.200
which we call as ‘talu’

00:28:26.200 --> 00:28:33.720
to connect it to the All-pervading&nbsp;
Power of Param Chaitanya.

00:28:33.720 --> 00:28:37.200
It is described as Ruha in Quran,

00:28:37.200 --> 00:28:47.560
it’s described as All-pervading&nbsp;
Power of divine love, in Torah.

00:28:47.560 --> 00:28:57.760
Also, it is described in the Bible&nbsp;
as the Cool Breeze of the Holy Ghost,

00:28:57.760 --> 00:29:03.160
whatever you may call it.

00:29:03.160 --> 00:29:14.960
The truth is that you are not this body,&nbsp;
this mind, these conditionings, this ego.

00:29:14.960 --> 00:29:19.840
Because you say, “This is my&nbsp;
ego, my conditioning, my body”.

00:29:19.840 --> 00:29:24.760
So, ‘my’ stands for which ‘I’?

00:29:24.760 --> 00:29:27.320
To whom does it belong?

00:29:29.480 --> 00:29:31.640
There must be someone.

00:29:31.640 --> 00:29:33.200
Now who runs your heart?

00:29:33.200 --> 00:29:37.320
If you ask a doctor, he’ll say&nbsp;
‘autonomous nervous system’.

00:29:37.320 --> 00:29:45.080
But who is the auto?

00:29:45.080 --> 00:29:51.720
So, the first truth is that&nbsp;
you are the pure Spirit, first.

00:29:51.720 --> 00:30:00.280
And the second truth is that there is&nbsp;
an All-pervading Power of divine love,

00:30:00.280 --> 00:30:03.560
which does all the living work.

00:30:03.560 --> 00:30:13.360
We see these beautiful flowers,&nbsp;
it’s a miracle by itself!

00:30:13.360 --> 00:30:19.400
If you see this human body-&nbsp;
doctors must be knowing-

00:30:19.400 --> 00:30:23.440
many questions we cannot answer.

00:30:23.440 --> 00:30:30.600
For example, any foreign body which&nbsp;
enters into the body is thrown away,

00:30:30.600 --> 00:30:32.680
it is the nature’s law.

00:30:32.680 --> 00:30:38.800
But when it’s the foetus, it is kept&nbsp;
there till 9 months nicely looked after,

00:30:38.800 --> 00:30:41.840
nourished, and then at the&nbsp;
right time, it is thrown away.

00:30:41.840 --> 00:30:44.760
How?

00:30:44.760 --> 00:30:47.720
There are many other things&nbsp;
which I can talk to doctors,

00:30:47.720 --> 00:30:56.000
but at this moment, we have to&nbsp;
understand that science is all right,

00:30:56.000 --> 00:31:00.000
but it cannot answer all the questions.

00:31:00.000 --> 00:31:02.760
First of all, it is amoral.

00:31:02.760 --> 00:31:05.600
Science is amoral

00:31:05.600 --> 00:31:11.720
and the second thing is that it&nbsp;
cannot answer many questions.

00:31:11.720 --> 00:31:19.360
One of them is why are we on this Earth?

00:31:19.360 --> 00:31:27.160
I’m sorry, we are having very marathon programs.

00:31:27.160 --> 00:31:36.520
[Shri Mataji is coughing]

00:31:36.520 --> 00:31:43.800
So, then we turn to religion, where is the answer?

00:31:43.800 --> 00:31:48.760
And then we see the chaos of the religion.

00:31:48.760 --> 00:31:54.360
In the name of God, what people are doing here?

00:31:54.360 --> 00:31:59.640
We can’t understand these people&nbsp;
who are in charge of religion,

00:31:59.640 --> 00:32:06.440
how can they be so corrupt, so money oriented?

00:32:06.440 --> 00:32:10.800
And absolutely without any morals.

00:32:10.800 --> 00:32:17.480
Any religion, it’s no question of&nbsp;
one religion or another religion.

00:32:17.480 --> 00:32:20.840
So, what we find basically,

00:32:20.840 --> 00:32:26.640
that all these religions are&nbsp;
either they are power oriented

00:32:26.640 --> 00:32:31.920
or they are money oriented or both.

00:32:31.920 --> 00:32:35.360
So, every intelligent man gets quite disillusioned

00:32:35.360 --> 00:32:38.000
and he doesn’t know what to do.

00:32:38.000 --> 00:32:41.320
What’s the use of following such a religion?

00:32:41.320 --> 00:32:49.160
It is absolutely a thing by&nbsp;
which you become an atheist.

00:32:49.160 --> 00:32:53.080
But it is unscientific to be an atheist,

00:32:53.080 --> 00:32:56.360
when you have not found out there is God or not.

00:32:56.360 --> 00:32:58.920
If you see, you say that you are atheist,

00:32:58.920 --> 00:33:01.800
you have not been scientific.

00:33:01.800 --> 00:33:04.720
First, find out if there is God or not.

00:33:04.720 --> 00:33:17.200
If you find it, then you have&nbsp;
to accept that there is God.

00:33:17.200 --> 00:33:25.880
Now Sahaja Yoga is not today’s discovery.

00:33:25.880 --> 00:33:30.120
It has been there for ages in our country.

00:33:30.120 --> 00:33:31.480
As there are many Indians,

00:33:31.480 --> 00:33:38.680
I would say this is your&nbsp;
heritage and ancient science.

00:33:38.680 --> 00:33:45.720
For example, we had three&nbsp;
types of seekings, in India.

00:33:45.720 --> 00:33:51.640
India has been really blessed by many seekers

00:33:51.640 --> 00:33:56.960
because the climate of that country is such.

00:33:58.640 --> 00:34:11.800
In their seeking, some of them followed&nbsp;
the way of finding about matter.

00:34:11.800 --> 00:34:16.440
So, they created Vedas.

00:34:16.440 --> 00:34:23.080
Another one was ‘bhakti’ because&nbsp;
they could not answer question.

00:34:23.080 --> 00:34:29.800
So, why not we worship God in&nbsp;
any form that we feel like?

00:34:29.800 --> 00:34:34.760
But the third one was in the centre

00:34:34.760 --> 00:34:44.240
where they talked of ‘atma&nbsp;
sakshatkar’, Self-realisation.

00:34:44.240 --> 00:34:52.560
Sitaji’s father, Raja Janaka, gave&nbsp;
Realization to one gentleman called Nachiketa,

00:34:52.560 --> 00:34:56.880
after taking his test for days together.

00:34:58.560 --> 00:35:01.800
This system existed more in Maharashtra

00:35:01.800 --> 00:35:08.040
where the Nath Panthis used to give Realization.

00:35:08.040 --> 00:35:11.080
But the tradition ‘parampara’ was such

00:35:11.080 --> 00:35:18.040
that one Guru will give&nbsp;
Realization to only one person.

00:35:18.040 --> 00:35:23.360
Till the time of Dnyaneshwara.

00:35:23.360 --> 00:35:26.800
His Guru was his own brother, Nivruttinath.

00:35:28.520 --> 00:35:32.080
But Dnyaneshwara took the&nbsp;
permission of his brother

00:35:32.080 --> 00:35:39.800
that, “At least, let me write&nbsp;
about how this works out”.

00:35:39.800 --> 00:35:45.200
Even in Gita, there’s no mention of Kundalini.

00:35:45.200 --> 00:35:51.240
But he wrote Dnyaneshwari, which is,&nbsp;
we can say, the explanation of Gita,

00:35:51.240 --> 00:35:56.800
in which in the sixth chapter,&nbsp;
he wrote clearly about Kundalini.

00:35:57.360 --> 00:36:01.000
But people at the helm of affairs,

00:36:01.000 --> 00:36:08.560
who did not know how to awaken&nbsp;
the Kundalini, or this power,

00:36:08.560 --> 00:36:13.480
said that this chapter is&nbsp;
‘nishiddha’ [prohibited],

00:36:13.480 --> 00:36:15.840
is not to be read.

00:36:15.840 --> 00:36:19.480
That’s how the whole thing went into oblivion

00:36:19.480 --> 00:36:26.720
and nobody even tried to find out&nbsp;
about this Kundalini awakening.

00:36:28.040 --> 00:36:34.040
But after the writing of Dnyanadeva,

00:36:34.040 --> 00:36:41.680
there was streams of saints who&nbsp;
came, who were Realized Souls.

00:36:41.680 --> 00:36:45.200
You heard the “Jogawa” of Namadeva.

00:36:45.200 --> 00:36:49.120
Namdev was in the 16th century [XIII].

00:36:49.120 --> 00:36:52.640
And what he says that, “Oh&nbsp;
Mother, give me the yoga,”

00:36:52.640 --> 00:36:56.240
means the union, “with this divine Power”.

00:36:56.240 --> 00:36:58.800
In every village you go, in&nbsp;
Maharashtra, they sing it,

00:36:58.800 --> 00:37:01.560
but they don’t know what it means.

00:37:01.560 --> 00:37:06.160
They are all asking for it, but&nbsp;
they don’t know what it means.

00:37:06.160 --> 00:37:18.960
And we had many, in every part of&nbsp;
India, every province, Realized souls.

00:37:18.960 --> 00:37:25.720
Namadeva went to Punjab where Guru&nbsp;
Nanaka very much honoured him,

00:37:25.720 --> 00:37:33.560
and he wrote about Kundalini,&nbsp;
about awakening, about Realization,

00:37:33.560 --> 00:37:39.400
in such a big book like that, in Punjabi language.

00:37:39.400 --> 00:37:42.440
Of course, Nanaka Sahib did a great job

00:37:42.440 --> 00:37:51.280
by taking all the poems or poetry of&nbsp;
all the saints who were Realized souls,

00:37:51.280 --> 00:37:57.080
and put them in Granth Sahib.

00:37:57.080 --> 00:38:01.160
But all their efforts failed.

00:38:01.160 --> 00:38:10.624
Kabira says, “Kaise samjhaun, sab jag andhaa?”

00:38:10.624 --> 00:38:10.680
[How to make them understand?&nbsp;
The whole world is blind].

00:38:10.680 --> 00:38:13.640
Also, when they started reading Granth Sahib,

00:38:13.640 --> 00:38:16.200
like Gita they read, they read Granth Sahib,

00:38:16.200 --> 00:38:20.040
they read, they think by reading.

00:38:20.040 --> 00:38:28.035
So Kabira has said, “Padhi&nbsp;
padhi panditha moorakh bhaye”

00:38:28.035 --> 00:38:28.080
[Reading, reading, the learned became fools].

00:38:28.080 --> 00:38:33.720
And in the sixth century&nbsp;
Adi Shankaracharya has said,

00:38:33.720 --> 00:38:37.880
“Mother, remove this shabda jalam [web of words].

00:38:37.880 --> 00:38:46.360
These webs of words take me away from you”.

00:38:46.360 --> 00:38:50.040
All these things were done;

00:38:50.040 --> 00:38:54.640
if you think I’ve done&nbsp;
anything about it, it’s this,

00:38:54.640 --> 00:39:00.320
that I worked out a system,

00:39:00.320 --> 00:39:06.880
or you can say, the permutations&nbsp;
and combinations of these chakras

00:39:06.880 --> 00:39:16.120
in such a way that a-mass&nbsp;
Realization can be given.

00:39:16.120 --> 00:39:17.480
A-mass Realization.

00:39:17.480 --> 00:39:19.240
It’s remarkable.

00:39:19.240 --> 00:39:22.480
First, of course, I started with one person.

00:39:22.480 --> 00:39:28.680
Then we had about 12 and now I&nbsp;
don’t know, we have in thousands.

00:39:28.680 --> 00:39:32.360
Russia, especially, is a very sensitive country.

00:39:32.360 --> 00:39:36.000
Not only Russia, but all the Eastern Block.

00:39:36.000 --> 00:39:41.960
In all these countries, we&nbsp;
have programs in the stadiums

00:39:41.960 --> 00:39:48.200
and never less than 16,000 people at least, never.

00:39:48.200 --> 00:39:51.640
America is very unfortunate that way.

00:39:51.640 --> 00:39:55.280
I don’t know about Indians in America.

00:39:55.280 --> 00:40:05.160
But the sensitivity to spirituality has&nbsp;
been dampened by the so-call freedom we had.

00:40:05.160 --> 00:40:09.640
And the materialism, which&nbsp;
made us everything gross,

00:40:09.640 --> 00:40:19.560
by this materialism our sensitivity&nbsp;
to spirituality has been dampened.

00:40:19.560 --> 00:40:24.800
Otherwise, for an Indian, his&nbsp;
‘mokha, his atma sakshatkar’

00:40:24.800 --> 00:40:32.720
was the highest goal, for anyone.

00:40:32.720 --> 00:40:33.600
How it was done?

00:40:33.600 --> 00:40:37.720
They used to go to gurus, this, that.

00:40:37.720 --> 00:40:41.480
But so many false gurus have come up

00:40:41.480 --> 00:40:46.800
as soon as they realized that in&nbsp;
this Kaliyuga, there are many seekers

00:40:46.800 --> 00:40:51.640
and that they can befool them, a market is there.

00:40:51.640 --> 00:40:56.360
So, they started marketing.

00:40:56.360 --> 00:41:01.040
We have to use our common sense.

00:41:01.040 --> 00:41:04.960
Spirituality, you can achieve through evolution

00:41:04.960 --> 00:41:12.800
which is a living process,&nbsp;
living process of your evolution.

00:41:12.800 --> 00:41:18.720
Now how much did we pay for our evolution?

00:41:18.720 --> 00:41:22.360
Now this Mother Earth gives us all these flowers.

00:41:22.360 --> 00:41:24.720
How much do we pay her?

00:41:24.720 --> 00:41:30.640
Nothing, because it’s a living process.

00:41:30.640 --> 00:41:36.280
So, Sahaja Yoga means, ‘sa’&nbsp;
means with; ‘ja’ means born.

00:41:36.280 --> 00:41:43.480
It’s the right to achieve&nbsp;
this union with the Divine.

00:41:43.480 --> 00:41:45.560
It’s your right.

00:41:45.560 --> 00:41:50.360
It’s a fundamental right,&nbsp;
especially for Indians, I would say,

00:41:50.360 --> 00:41:53.760
because you are from the Yoga Bhoomi.

00:41:53.760 --> 00:41:56.240
We are from the Yoga Bhoomi.

00:41:57.520 --> 00:42:04.560
And this is your fundamental&nbsp;
right to get your Realization.

00:42:04.560 --> 00:42:09.320
But it cannot be forced.

00:42:09.320 --> 00:42:12.480
You have to choose it.

00:42:12.480 --> 00:42:16.200
You have to ask for it.

00:42:16.200 --> 00:42:21.680
You have to have pure desire to get it.

00:42:21.680 --> 00:42:26.160
This is the power of pure desire&nbsp;
which we call as Kundalini.

00:42:27.480 --> 00:42:32.160
She is your individual mother.

00:42:32.160 --> 00:42:34.717
She knows all about you.

00:42:34.717 --> 00:42:39.040
It is all recorded, taped as if, all about you,

00:42:39.040 --> 00:42:43.480
whatever you have done, whatever your desires are,

00:42:43.480 --> 00:42:47.880
it’s all being taped.

00:42:47.880 --> 00:42:54.720
And this mother of yours is anxious&nbsp;
to give you your second birth.

00:42:54.720 --> 00:42:59.080
As in Sanskrit, you know, a Realized&nbsp;
soul is called as ‘dvijaha’,

00:42:59.080 --> 00:43:00.160
born twice,

00:43:00.160 --> 00:43:03.560
and a bird is also called as ‘dvijaha’

00:43:03.560 --> 00:43:08.560
meaning it’s an egg first,&nbsp;
and then a bird it becomes.

00:43:08.560 --> 00:43:11.640
In the same way, we are first human beings

00:43:11.640 --> 00:43:16.000
and then we become enlightened souls.

00:43:16.000 --> 00:43:21.160
What doctor Wells has told you is nothing&nbsp;
compared to what can happen to you.

00:43:21.160 --> 00:43:23.920
Because it is your own power.

00:43:23.920 --> 00:43:26.080
It’s your own.

00:43:27.440 --> 00:43:31.160
And you are not aware how fantastic you are.

00:43:31.160 --> 00:43:36.080
You don’t know how many&nbsp;
powers there are within you.

00:43:36.080 --> 00:43:39.720
That’s why we do not value it.

00:43:39.720 --> 00:43:44.880
For example, this instrument is made&nbsp;
and is not connected to the mains:

00:43:44.880 --> 00:43:47.560
it has no identity, it has no meaning.

00:43:47.560 --> 00:43:54.960
It won’t work, unless and until&nbsp;
we are connected to the mains.

00:43:54.960 --> 00:43:59.640
We have no idea, we are not aware at all

00:43:59.640 --> 00:44:04.840
as to what we are, how fantastic we could be,

00:44:04.840 --> 00:44:09.800
what we can do to ourselves and to others.

00:44:09.800 --> 00:44:16.560
It is very important for all of&nbsp;
us to get this Self-realization,

00:44:16.560 --> 00:44:19.800
otherwise, there will be&nbsp;
only two status of people:

00:44:19.800 --> 00:44:25.080
those who are Self-realized others who are not.

00:44:25.080 --> 00:44:34.640
And as you see, the destructive forces&nbsp;
are working in America of yours.

00:44:34.640 --> 00:44:40.080
How many diseases you have of&nbsp;
which we had never heard before?

00:44:40.080 --> 00:44:44.480
Every time you come, you find&nbsp;
a new disease coming out.

00:44:44.480 --> 00:44:47.960
All these destructive forces,&nbsp;
only on physical level,

00:44:47.960 --> 00:44:51.040
then on mental level,

00:44:51.040 --> 00:44:56.400
and then on spiritual level.

00:44:56.400 --> 00:45:03.000
So, on one side a man is&nbsp;
getting destroyed from within.

00:45:03.000 --> 00:45:05.440
On the other side, from within,

00:45:05.440 --> 00:45:14.920
he is going to ascend and achieve eternal life.

00:45:14.920 --> 00:45:20.000
As a result of this happening, what you get,

00:45:20.000 --> 00:45:25.880
first you start feeling on your&nbsp;
fingertips this All-pervading Power.

00:45:27.880 --> 00:45:30.880
For the first time, you feel it.

00:45:30.880 --> 00:45:34.360
You have never felt this&nbsp;
All-pervading Power before.

00:45:34.360 --> 00:45:38.240
For the first time, you start feeling it.

00:45:38.240 --> 00:45:45.360
And also you start feeling this&nbsp;
coming out of your fontanel bone area,

00:45:45.360 --> 00:45:47.320
the cool breeze of the Holy Ghost.

00:45:47.320 --> 00:45:48.880
You see, you feel it.

00:45:48.880 --> 00:45:53.200
It’s an experience it is not&nbsp;
just a lecture or a sermon.

