01:06:19.640 --> 01:06:25.540
And this All-pervading Power&nbsp;
is the ocean of forgiveness.

01:06:25.540 --> 01:06:32.720
And whatever wrong you have done can&nbsp;
be easily dissolved by that ocean.

01:06:32.720 --> 01:06:36.960
So, now don’t think that you&nbsp;
are guilty by any chance.

01:06:36.960 --> 01:06:41.160
But physically, from science&nbsp;
point of view, it is different.

01:06:41.160 --> 01:06:44.400
But from Sahaja Yoga point of view,

01:06:44.400 --> 01:06:50.600
if you feel guilty you get the center&nbsp;
on the left-hand side of the Vishuddhi

01:06:50.600 --> 01:06:52.720
in a jeopardy, in trouble.

01:06:52.720 --> 01:06:58.080
And once you get this center caught&nbsp;
up, you might get spondylitis.

01:06:58.080 --> 01:07:01.960
You might get angina.

01:07:01.960 --> 01:07:05.160
Angina is because of that, angina.

01:07:05.160 --> 01:07:09.840
Thirdly, you might get lethargic organs.

01:07:09.840 --> 01:07:11.920
It’s a very serious thing.

01:07:11.920 --> 01:07:21.920
So, why to have those serious things&nbsp;
in ourselves by feeling guilty?

01:07:21.920 --> 01:07:28.080
As the men are women also feel guilty&nbsp;
for something very, very trivial.

01:07:28.080 --> 01:07:31.080
But what a serious thing that happens!

01:07:31.080 --> 01:07:47.600
So, please don’t feel guilty at&nbsp;
all, not at all, about anything.

01:07:47.600 --> 01:07:50.720
Especially at this moment,&nbsp;
when the Kundalini is rising,

01:07:50.720 --> 01:07:53.920
and you are- this center is catching.

01:07:56.000 --> 01:08:06.000
Then it won’t go through this centre.

01:08:06.000 --> 01:08:13.480
Nowadays also, people think&nbsp;
that if they starve themselves,

01:08:13.480 --> 01:08:21.360
or if they stand on their&nbsp;
heads, or maybe go to Himalayas,

01:08:21.360 --> 01:08:23.840
they will get Realization. No.

01:08:27.680 --> 01:08:31.280
God is your father.

01:08:31.280 --> 01:08:38.600
He is ocean of compassion, why&nbsp;
would he like you to suffer?

01:08:38.600 --> 01:08:46.400
Think of any father who makes his child suffer?

01:08:46.400 --> 01:08:56.640
So, also, this idea of fasting and&nbsp;
all this this suffering is all absurd.

01:08:56.640 --> 01:08:59.160
Some people talk of karmas.

01:08:59.160 --> 01:09:03.400
When this center opens, on&nbsp;
the optic chiasma, like this,

01:09:03.400 --> 01:09:05.360
all your karmas are sucked in.

01:09:05.360 --> 01:09:10.000
Doctor can show them, on the yellow side.

01:09:10.000 --> 01:09:12.320
These are all your karmas your ego.

01:09:12.320 --> 01:09:16.040
And the left-side are your conditionings.

01:09:16.040 --> 01:09:18.840
They are all sucked in.

01:09:18.840 --> 01:09:21.960
So, you become ‘akarmis’ |[without any karma].

01:09:21.960 --> 01:09:25.360
Only the human beings think&nbsp;
that they have done karmas.

01:09:25.360 --> 01:09:31.160
The dogs and the tigers don’t think,

01:09:31.160 --> 01:09:34.240
because they are ‘pashu’, they are&nbsp;
in the ‘pash’ [control] of God,

01:09:34.240 --> 01:09:35.600
so they don’t think.

01:09:35.600 --> 01:09:36.600
We have freedom.

01:09:36.600 --> 01:09:43.440
So, we think we have done this wrong,&nbsp;
that wrong, or our ego sometimes,

01:09:43.440 --> 01:09:45.400
“I am this, I am that”.

01:09:45.400 --> 01:09:49.880
All that is sucked in by the Kundalini.

01:09:49.880 --> 01:09:53.720
I’m just removing some of&nbsp;
your thoughts which are there.

01:09:57.240 --> 01:10:01.840
So, please don’t try in any way to&nbsp;
condemn yourself or judge yourself.

01:10:01.840 --> 01:10:07.080
Let the Kundalini judge, she knows.

01:10:07.080 --> 01:10:11.640
And as the mother that you had gave you birth,

01:10:11.640 --> 01:10:14.320
taking all the trouble upon herself,

01:10:14.320 --> 01:10:19.320
this Kundalini doesn’t trouble you at all.

01:10:19.320 --> 01:10:22.600
She very delicately, beautifully, rises

01:10:22.600 --> 01:10:29.080
and pierces through this fontanel bone area.

01:10:29.080 --> 01:10:36.960
And you get the actualization of your&nbsp;
baptism, or your state of second birth.

01:10:36.960 --> 01:10:39.280
Actualization, again.

01:10:39.280 --> 01:10:45.200
In Sahaja Yoga, we don’t have to say, “Don’t&nbsp;
do something”, as doctor has told you.

01:10:45.200 --> 01:10:48.120
You just automatically become that.

01:10:48.120 --> 01:10:51.200
Automatically, you become righteous.

01:10:51.200 --> 01:10:52.760
Nothing is to be said, “Don’t do”.

01:10:52.760 --> 01:10:55.600
Nothing, it just happens.

01:10:55.600 --> 01:10:59.640
For this, I have to give&nbsp;
you a very simple example.

01:10:59.640 --> 01:11:03.880
If you have a snake in your&nbsp;
hand, say, I’m holding a snake

01:11:03.880 --> 01:11:05.560
and I’m an obstinate person.

01:11:05.560 --> 01:11:06.760
There is darkness.

01:11:06.760 --> 01:11:10.800
Somebody says, “This is a snake”.

01:11:10.800 --> 01:11:13.680
I’ll say, “No, it is a rope”.

01:11:13.680 --> 01:11:17.000
Till the snake bites me, I’ll say, “It’s a rope”.

01:11:17.000 --> 01:11:22.680
But if there is little light,&nbsp;
I’ll just throw it away myself.

01:11:22.680 --> 01:11:23.920
Nobody has to tell me anything.

01:11:23.920 --> 01:11:27.240
In this way, it happens.

01:11:27.240 --> 01:11:30.080
So, please have no guilt.

01:11:30.080 --> 01:11:33.760
And the third condition is even simple.

01:11:33.760 --> 01:11:37.240
It’s to forgive everyone, in general,

01:11:37.240 --> 01:11:40.560
without thinking of the people&nbsp;
whom you have to forgive.

01:11:40.560 --> 01:11:45.080
Now here, people will say, “It’s&nbsp;
very difficult”. Many people say.

01:11:45.080 --> 01:11:53.640
Logically, whether you forgive&nbsp;
or don’t forgive, what do you do?

01:11:53.640 --> 01:11:56.000
It’s a myth.

01:11:56.000 --> 01:11:59.840
You don’t do anything, it’s a myth.

01:11:59.840 --> 01:12:03.960
But if you don’t forgive, then&nbsp;
you play into wrong hands.

01:12:03.960 --> 01:12:11.960
Those who try to trouble you are&nbsp;
happy, but you are torturing yourself.

01:12:11.960 --> 01:12:16.200
But at this moment, especially,&nbsp;
the center of Agnya,

01:12:16.200 --> 01:12:21.200
which is like this, like a&nbsp;
cross, is absolutely constricted.

01:12:21.200 --> 01:12:23.480
If you don’t forgive, it will never open.

01:12:25.160 --> 01:12:29.640
Just to feel that, “I forgive&nbsp;
everyone” without thinking about them,

01:12:29.640 --> 01:12:30.960
it opens.

01:12:30.960 --> 01:12:33.480
And then the Kundalini will rise.

01:12:33.480 --> 01:12:36.760
As it is, you have tortured&nbsp;
yourself by not forgiving.

01:12:36.760 --> 01:12:41.160
And now, at this moment,&nbsp;
please, don’t miss the point.

01:12:41.160 --> 01:12:45.680
Just you have to say, “I forgive everyone”,

01:12:45.680 --> 01:12:50.680
without even thinking about them, in general.

01:12:50.680 --> 01:12:57.480
I hope I have been able to convince&nbsp;
you logically what is important.

01:12:57.480 --> 01:13:01.760
These are the only three simple conditions.

01:13:01.760 --> 01:13:07.800
And now, we’ll show you how we will&nbsp;
nourish our centres, on the left-hand side.

01:13:07.800 --> 01:13:10.080
And then you have to close your eyes,

01:13:10.080 --> 01:13:14.640
and again we have to do the same&nbsp;
thing, which is very simple.

01:13:14.640 --> 01:13:21.014
Again I say, it’s nothing difficult.

01:13:21.014 --> 01:13:21.040
[Self-realisation process]

01:13:21.040 --> 01:13:28.080
So, please, understand there&nbsp;
are two powers, left and right,

01:13:28.080 --> 01:13:32.000
so both the feet should apart from each other.

01:13:32.000 --> 01:13:36.640
And left hand should be&nbsp;
comfortably placed on your lap.

01:13:36.640 --> 01:13:38.920
You have to sit comfortably.

01:13:38.920 --> 01:13:40.800
I told you, you don’t have to go to Himalayas,

01:13:40.800 --> 01:13:44.160
here on your seat, you’ll get your Realisation.

